</a>
<div class="quoteText">

        &ldquo;Two things are infinite: the universe and human stupidity; and I&apos;m not sure about the universe.&rdquo;
    <br />
  &#8213;
  <span class="authorOrTitle">
    Albert Einstein
  </span>
</div>


